l; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Vigência contratual</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">12 meses, prorrogável por até 5 anos.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Exigência de visita técnica?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Facultativa, mas recomendada. Deve ser agendada pelo telefone (79) 3632-2107.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Data prevista para início dos serviços</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Não especificada. Após assinatura do contrato, que deve ocorrer em até 5 dias úteis após homologação.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Exigência de garantia?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;"><b>Sim, garantia de 5% do valor anual do contrato (caução, seguro-garantia ou fiança bancária).</b></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Edital regido por alguma legislação específica?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Sim: Lei nº 13.303/2016, Decreto nº 8.945/2016, Lei nº 14.133/2021 (para procedimentos da sessão pública), RLCE 2.0 da EBSERH.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Unidade de medida</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Plantão de 24h</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Volumetria total prevista</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">1.098 plantões/ano (estimativa)</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Volumetria mensal</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;"><b><font color="#dc2626" style="background-color: rgb(254, 240, 138);">Aproximadamente 21 plantões/semana × 4,33 = ~91 plantões/mês (média)</font></b></td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Volumetria anual</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">1.098 plantões</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Necessidade de retorno?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Não se aplica (serviço contínuo, sem retorno de consultas).</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Necessidade de equipamentos/materiais?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Sim: a contratada deve fornecer e instalar registrador de ponto eletrônico biométrico (off-line), além de arcar com custos de instalação e manutenção.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Exige atestado de capacidade técnica?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Sim, com experiência mínima de 12 meses na execução de objeto compatível.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Médicos precisam ter RQE?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Sim, exige-se Registro de Qualificação de Especialista (RQE) em Cirurgia Geral.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Responsável técnico precisa ter RQE?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Sim, o responsável técnico deve ser especialista em Cirurgia Geral com RQE reconhecido pela AMB ou CNRM.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Exige vínculo CLT?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Não especifica CLT, mas exige vínculo comprovado (empregatício, societário ou contrato de prestação de serviços).</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">CNDs exigidas</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Certidões Negativas de: Débitos Federais (RFB/PGFN), FGTS (CRF), Trabalhista (CNDT), Falência, entre outras.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Exige CNES?</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Não mencionado.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Outros documentos técnicos</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">Certificado de Regularidade do CRM da empresa, declaração de compromisso de registro no CRM-SE (se for de outro estado), declaração de responsável técnico, atestados de serviços prestados, comprovação de quadro permanente.</td></tr><tr><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 16px 10px 0px;"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Observações Relevantes</span></td><td style="border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12); font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 15px; line-height: 25px; min-width: 100px; max-width: min(30vw, 320px); padding: 10px 0px 10px 16px;">- Objeto é considerado complexo, justificando afastamento da preferência para ME/EPP.<br>- Exige preceptoria de residentes e estudantes, integrando ensino e assistência.<br>- Contratação por preço unitário, com pagamento conforme quantitativo executado.<br>- Sistema de medição de resultados (IMR) com possibilidade de glosa e penalidades.<br>- Vedação a subcontratação.<br>- Exigência de ponto eletrônico biométrico próprio da contratada.<br>- Sustentabilidade ambiental e social integrada ao contrato</td></tr></tbody></table><br><br></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, 'descarte_edital', 'c9d41fe7-f0dc-4941-8491-59e9551a81d8', NULL, '2025-12-18T14:48:18.297Z', '2026-02-09T18:07:20.552Z', '7156440', 'Lagarto', 'Pregão Eletrônico', '2026-01-12T12:00:00.000Z', '{"REPETIDO"}', 'n8n', '7156440', 'PE 90058/2025 LAGARTO/SE', '{}', false, false, false, false, false, false, '{}', NULL, 'GSS', NULL, false, 'MODALIDADE', NULL, NULL),
